@229=~Once exposed to air, this oil will immediately burst into flame, inflicting 5D6 points of damage (save vs. spell for half) to all within the immediate area around the potion. It can be hurled up to 40 feet, at which point it hits the ground and immediately explodes into a ball of fire.

