Area: 30-feet cube
Range: 40 feet~

@230=~This potion increases the movement capabilities of the imbiber by 100%. Thus, a movement rate of 9 becomes 18. A hasted creature gains a -2 initiative bonus. This does not reduce spellcasting time, however. The duration of the effect is 1 turn.

