@231=~Close examination reveals this liquid to be very peculiar in nature. It could be a sorcerer's dream, but that would depend entirely on who you asked. After ingesting the mixture, the drinker becomes the weakest, most unwise, yet incredibly intelligent person to have ever lived, with an innate 50% magical damage resistance as well. The effects remain for an entire 24 hours, so think carefully before unplugging the cork.

