@232=~This is one of the oddest potions you have ever examined. Once drank, this mixture causes one's muscles to immediately bulge to completely inhuman proportions, titan-like actually, while dexterity and constitution are both reduced essentially to that of a slug. The effect lasts for a full 24 hours, so think carefully before quaffing this suspect drink.

STATISTICS:

Strength: 25
Dexterity: 3
Constitution: 3
Duration: 24 hours~

@233=~The Elixir of Health is a powerful healing mixture designed to cleanse the body of all impurities. It cures all poisons and diseases. It will not heal wounds or restore hit points.

STATISTICS:

Cures: Poison, disease and drunkenness~

@234=~Potion of Absorption, Bludgeoning~

@235=~This potion, as would be expected, will absorb external attacks once it has been consumed. All blunt attacks made against the imbiber are cushioned, so that only the strongest get through. This potion is not cumulative with itself.

