Duration: 1 turn~

@236=~This potion will raise the dexterity of the imbiber to 18, effecting armor class and missile attack adjustment for the duration of the effect, in this case 1 turn.

STATISTICS:

Dexterity: 18
Duration: 1 turn~

@237=~As the name implies, this potion will neutralize any poison of which the imbiber is currently suffering the effects. In addition, the user becomes completely immune to poisons from creatures with 3 HD or less, and gains a +2 bonus to all saving throws vs. poison. The cleansing is instant and the potion may only be used once.

