Damage: 6D6 (save vs. breath for half)
Area: 30-feet radius
Range: 40 feet~

@241=~By drinking the potion of firebreath, it magically transforms the throat so that it is capable of a giant breath of fire spewing forth in an arc. The effect does 5D10 damage to the target with an allowed save vs. breath weapon for half.

STATISTICS:

Damage: 5D10 (save vs. breath weapon for half)~

@242=~Once consumed, this potion will cause a surge of energy to travel through the body raising the drinker's constitution to 18. This provides all the bonuses of having a high constitution such as hit points for the duration of the effect, which is 1 turn.

STATISTICS:

Constitution: 18
Duration: 1 turn~

@243=~Very much as the name implies, this potion will increase the intelligence of the imbiber by 4 points up to a maximum of 25. The duration is 8 rounds. This potion is not cumulative with itself.

