@272=~A Protection from Magic scroll invokes a very powerful, invisible globe of anti-magic in a 3' radius from the target. No form of magic can pass into or out of it but physical matter is not hindered. This will remove spell effects that the caster is currently under. The effect is not permanent, however, and will wear off within 1 turn.

