@285=~This clerical weapon appears to be a normal wooden staff of the type used when trekking in the wilderness. It gives off a very faint aura of alteration magic. Upon identification of the command word, the staff takes on the attributes of a mace, which allow it to be wielded with one hand. This was designed for both priests and druids.

