@286=~When this seemingly ordinary quarterstaff is examined magically, it has an aura of alteration. Upon command, a long sharp spear-blade will shoot forth from its upper end, making the staff into a spear. This weapon was designed mainly for priests and wizards, although it is usable by anybody.

