Special: 2 magic missiles will strike target
Damage: 1D4 + 1 per missile
Range: 100 feet~

@290=~When used, this wand shoots forth a thin ray of bluish color to a maximum range of 60 feet. When a creature is touched by the ray, it must roll a save vs. wands in order to avoid being stunned for 10 rounds.

