Range: 100 ft
Duration: 10 rounds
Usable by:
 Mage~
 
@291=~The wand will cough forth a huge, burning ball of fire that streaks out to the desired range (to a maximum of 120') and bursts in a fiery, violent blast, just like the fireball spell. The fireball inflicts 6d6 + 6 points of damage. The victim(s) may make a save vs. wands in order to take only half damage.

STATISTICS:

Special: Fireball
