@520=~Ring of Warmth: 'Vifrosd's Glow'
Vifrosd, a druid of the Spine of the World Mountains, is the first person known to possess this ring. He found it on a plateau north of the mountain range, a field littered with small frozen lakes. Here he came upon one lake in which the water was not frozen, and in fact, slightly warm to the touch. The water was clear and something in the middle of the lake caught his attention. A quick search revealed this ring lying on a stone at the bottom of the lake. He took it and stepped out of the water, just in time to hear it freeze behind him as he did so. Awed by its power, he quickly put it on and felt the numbing cold of the surrounding lands leave his body.

