@814=~Fire Aura 
(Abjuration)

Level: 4
Range: 0
Duration: 4 rounds/level
Casting Time: 4
Area of Effect: Caster
Saving Throw: None

By means of this spell, the caster surrounds his body with an aura of magical green fire. The Fire Aura provides complete immunity to all forms of fire, both natural and magical; the flames can be extinguished only by Dispel Magic or a similar spell.~ 

@815=~Improved Strength~ 

@816=~Improved Strength 
(Alteration)

Level: 4
Range: Touch
Duration: 1 round/level
Casting Time: 4
Area of Effect: Creature touched
