Range: 10 yards
Duration: 1 day
Casting Time: 1 round
Area of Effect: Special
Saving Throw: None

This spell creates the lowest of the undead monsters: skeletons and zombies, usually from the bones of dead humans, demihumans, or humanoids. The spell causes these remains to become animated and obey the simple telepathic commands of the caster, regardless of how they communicated in life. They will not responds to verbal or magical commands from enemies, making them immune to mind-control magics such as Charm or Domination, and as well, having no eyes, flesh, internal organs or cardiopulmonary systems, are immune to poison and petrification. The undead remain animated until they are destroyed in combat, 24 hours pass, or are turned; the magic cannot be dispelled. The wizard can animate one skeleton for each experience level he has attained, or one zombie for every two levels.~ 

