@973=~This plate mail has been expertly crafted by Taerom Fuiruim of Beregost. Sheathed in the chitinous scales of the ankheg, it provides a greater degree of protection than traditional plate mail and is not susceptible to rust. As any world-weary adventurer will tell you, however, the most appreciated aspect of ankheg mail is its light weight and low encumbrance, being only half the weight of normal plate mail. Monsters come and go but fatigue is a constant enemy.

