Level: 5
Sphere: Guardian
Range: 0
Duration: 1 round/level
Casting Time: 9
Area of Effect: The caster
Saving Throw: None 

This spell grants the priest 2% magic resistance per level of the priest, to a maximum of 40%, for the spell's duration.  This magic resistance functions identically to the magic resistance possessed by certain monsters and bestowed by certain magical items.~

