Level: 2
Range: 30 yards
Duration: Special
Casting Time: 2
Area of Effect: 20-ft. cube
Saving Throw: Special

This spell creates a cloud of glittering golden particles within the area of effect. Those in the area must roll a successful saving throw vs. spell or be blinded (-4 penalties to attack rolls and Armor Class) for 3 rounds. In addition, all within the area are covered by the dust, which cannot be removed and continues to sparkle until it fades. Note that this reveals invisible creatures and prevents hiding in shadows. The dust fades in 2 rounds plus 1 round per caster level.~

